<br>
&quot;What beautiful art this whole ordeal will turn out. Poetry, Song , Dance. I mean if we really wanted to, we could even make a nice comedic play out of this!&quot; Apollo chuckled a bit, shaking the hair from his eyes.<br>
<br>
