<br>
&quot;I know what is to come of this. This my dears, is a lose, lose situation. Either way, something catastrophic is bound to happen. There are times in the life of immortal and man where one has to just let things take their course. This is one of those things. So please, do not let this put a twist in your toga.&quot; Apollo smiled and patted the head of Calliope with a chuckle, and scurried off to cohort with Aphrodite. <p>      *~*The Golden God*~*
